high_descs: Go straight and turn right and walk towards the cabinet.
Pick up the apple from the cabinet rack.
Turn right, walk, and turn left, head to the microwave.
Put the apple into the microwave, heat it up, and pick it up back.
Turn left and walk, again turn left and walk towards the fridge.
Put the apple in the last rack of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right to the kitchen counters and look down at the cabinets.
Remove the whole apple from the cabinet below the counter with another apple on top of it.
Take the apple from the cabinet to the microwave to the right of the counters.
Use the microwave on the apple.
Turn left and go ahead to the fridge on the left.
Place the apple in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Microwave a whole apple and place it in a fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and head straight towards the cabinet
Open cabinet and take apple from it
Turn around and head straight, the hang left towards the microwave
Put apple inside the oven and heat it and take it out
Turn left and head straight, the hang left towards the fridge
anns.task_desc: Heating the apple and cooling it down
